src:
Hasil FP1 MotoGP Malaysia: Quartararo Tercepat, Trio Yamaha Terdepan
01 Nov 2019, 10:50 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Pebalap Petronas Yamaha SRT, Fabio Quartararo, sukses mencatatkan waktu tercepat dalam sesi latihan bebas pertama (FP1) MotoGP Malaysia di Sirkuit Sepang pada Jumat (1/11/2019).
Pebalap Prancis ini diikuti oleh tandemnya, Franco Morbidelli, di posisi kedua, dan pebalap Monster Energy Yamaha, Maverick Vinales, di posisi ketiga.
Sementara itu posisi keempat dan kelima masing-masing ditempati oleh pebalap Repsol Honda, Marc Marquez, dan pebalap Ducati Team, Andrea Dovizioso.
Berikut hasil FP1 MotoGP Malaysia 2019.
text:
Malaysian MotoGP FP1 Results: Fastest Quartararo, Yamaha Trio Leading
Nov 1, 2019, 10:50 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Yamaha SRT Petronas racer, Fabio Quartararo, successfully recorded the fastest time in the first free practice session (FP1) Malaysian MotoGP at the Sepang Circuit on Friday (1/11/2019).
The Frenchman was followed by his tandem, Franco Morbidelli, in second place, and Monster Energy Yamaha racer, Maverick Vinales, in third position.
Meanwhile the fourth and fifth positions were each occupied by Repsol Honda rider Marc Marquez and Ducati Team rider Andrea Dovizioso.
Following are the results of the 2019 Malaysian MotoGP FP1.
